claimer stays at the bottom while she continues speaking, ending with a bright, direct smile.\n\nThe final image is a teal product package or product card filling the screen. A green banner at the upper left says “NEW.” Near the top is the Always circular logo, with a pink and dark teal swirl inside. Large white text reads “always with CHANNELS,” and a dark teal band across the lower portion reads “MAXI with WINGS.” The packaging uses clean, bold white lettering against the turquoise background, presenting the product name clearly.",
